Vendor/product offerings ought to be distinct public software products, modules, hosted offerings, or open-source projects. Generic databases, BI tools, warehouses, iPaaS platforms, ETL platforms, broad cloud products, and broad data companies count only when the cited page frames the submitted product or offering around importing, mapping, validating, transforming, ingesting, migrating, or onboarding external/customer business data.

