- `data_handling_or_trust`: product-specific data-custody, security, privacy, compliance, hosting, self-hosting, data-residency, retention, encryption, SOC 2/HIPAA/GDPR, or comparable trust posture for imported/onboarded/customer data or the product's ingestion, mapping, validation, connector, or deployment flow.
